docs.text: Įvairios skaičiuoklės RunningAHEAD - Pace Calculator VO2max Calculator There are four VO2max calculators on this page. Each VO2max calculator provides an estimate of your VO2max. The first calculator does not require any physical exertion and is very quick and reliable. The second, third, and fourth calculators estimate your VO2max based on your performance of a unique physical exertion test. Scroll through the entire page to view them all! Fitness calculator Joe Friel's Quick Guide to Setting Zones Race Equivalency Calculator
